  "keyFeatures": [
    "Recipe catalog with health category filtering, full-text search, and detailed nutritional data",
    "NutriBot — AI chatbot powered by Groq (LLaMA 3.3 70B) that recommends recipes based on user health profile and dietary restrictions",
    "Daily nutrition tracking with calorie and macro summaries by day, week, and month",
    "Personalized nutritional recommendations using TDEE/BMR calculations and health conditions",
    "Favorites system with real-time sync to MongoDB",
    "Google OAuth and email/password authentication with email verification",
    "User health profile (conditions, categories, allergies, preferences) that drives AI and recommendations",
    "Admin dashboard with user management, ban system, recipe CRUD, bulk import/export, review image moderation, and terms management",
    "PDF export of recipe selections",
    "Dark mode support",
    "Rate limiting, XSS sanitization, Helmet security headers, and account lockout protection"
  ],
